        <para id="id11385210">STEPS 3 and 4</para>
        <para id="id14014866">Divide into groups and follow the teacher’s instructions.</para>
        <para id="id16926493">The colour tone changes because <emphasis effect="bold">harmony </emphasis>is created. The same harmony is  used throughout.</para>
